captions.text: Mo-ment of truth.

Why can't I figure out what's wrong?
Why won't you move?
Here's the kick... Goooaaalll!!
Sorry, hope I didn't break anything...

Three months of intense work, Max!
That's what you broke!!
Oh, wow!... Alex, this is awesome!

Tug my leash... It! Is! Working!!! Max... You
brought him to life! How can I ever thank you?!
Don't worry about it. Later!

You know? I would love to go out and play
soccer... instead of cleaning this mess.
I'll do that for you. It's the least I could do.

Hey. Listen... I'm supposed to do
the dishes... But could you...
Of course.
Cool. I'm going out.

Alex.. My shoes are breaking...
and I was wondering,

would you glue them back
together for me, huh?
I'm kind of busy here, Max...

Fine. That's cool. By the
way... how's your robot?

He's lookin' pretty awesome.
Your finest work. And

uh who got him to work right? Oh, yeah, I did.
But I guess it's no big deal. Nyah! Who cares?!

Give me your broken sneakers.
They'll be ready in half an hour.

It might take longer... because this one
needs to be restitched on both sides.

Alex! Help me with my science
project, like I helped with yours.

Hey Alex, could you clear out of your room
for like a couple of hours? I've got a match

tomorrow I need to practice my returns. And can
you move all your stuff? It gets in my way.

I've had it!! A few favors was
reasonable but I am finished!!
Oh, you are?! And did you forget about-

Take it, it's all yours! It's not worth it!
Take it and get out!

Yeah, yeah, yeah, nerd-face! Talk about...
ungrateful. Stupid thing

didn't even work until I knocked it
over... big smart guy! Turbo-nerd-
Help me! Helllppp!!!

You alright? Looks like you need help.
Alex?!
I'll pull it off. Relax...

No! I'm fine. I meant to do this.
It's an experiment.
But you yelled (BACK/SIDE) for help!

That was a test. My theory is...
if big-eared aliens

attack, drum-headed soldiers
could be our best defense...
Are you... alright, Maxy?

Sure. Thank you. Well... Go ahead and give
me the list of stuff I have to do for you...

What are you talking about? I'm just glad
you're alright. No payback required.

Uh... please forgive me, Alex. I was a jerk. And
you still helped me. Seriously... that was classy.
This is yours.

Nah you keep him, because I started working on
something even better: a flying smart-phone.
But it... doesn't quite fly yet.
Awesome!!
Whoa, be careful! It is very delicate!!

No. No. This thing is your invention, Alex.
I'm just the super-cool

test pilot who's brave enough to
find out if your stuff's working.
Sounds right!
